[
	{
		"id": 0,
		"localized_name": "鬼門",
		"romanized_name": "Kimon",
		"model_path_hash": "4093314950907503731",
		"text": "皆様方……今まで隠していて、ごめんなさい！\n拙者……実は……なんと……",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_181_504_00611",
		"still_path_hash": "6299303620813546084",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 1,
		"localized_name": "鬼門",
		"romanized_name": "Kimon",
		"model_path_hash": "4093314950907503731",
		"text": "忍びの家の出なのでありまする！\n今日は一族に伝わる忍術をお見せいたしましょう！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_181_504_00612",
		"still_path_hash": "6299303620813546084",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 2,
		"localized_name": "イザナ",
		"romanized_name": "Izana",
		"model_path_hash": "3787596258689044991",
		"text": "わあ……！　忍術って、どんななんだろう……！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_048_504_00613",
		"still_path_hash": "4716347634718713212",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 3,
		"localized_name": "ヨハナ",
		"romanized_name": "Johanna",
		"model_path_hash": "5020305352148956270",
		"text": "きっと、マジックみたいなものでしょ。\nどうせ大したことは――",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_004_504_00614",
		"still_path_hash": "9072463264798612382",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 4,
		"localized_name": "鬼門",
		"romanized_name": "Kimon",
		"model_path_hash": "4093314950907503731",
		"text": "忍法・口寄せの術！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_181_504_00615",
		"still_path_hash": "6299303620813546084",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 5,
		"localized_name": "イザナ",
		"romanized_name": "Izana",
		"model_path_hash": "3787596258689044991",
		"text": "ええーっ！？　どこから！？",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_048_504_00616",
		"still_path_hash": "4716347634718713212",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 6,
		"localized_name": "ヨハナ",
		"romanized_name": "Johanna",
		"model_path_hash": "5020305352148956270",
		"text": "なっ！？　なにこれ！　すごいじゃない！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_004_504_00617",
		"still_path_hash": "9072463264798612382",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 7,
		"localized_name": "鬼門",
		"romanized_name": "Kimon",
		"model_path_hash": "4093314950907503731",
		"text": "まだまだありまする！　シュッ！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_181_504_00618",
		"still_path_hash": "6299303620813546084",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 8,
		"localized_name": "鬼門",
		"romanized_name": "Kimon",
		"model_path_hash": "4093314950907503731",
		"text": "これが縮地の術！　ライブでもステージの端から端まで\n一瞬で移動できまする！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_181_504_00619",
		"still_path_hash": "6299303620813546084",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 9,
		"localized_name": "ヨハナ",
		"romanized_name": "Johanna",
		"model_path_hash": "5020305352148956270",
		"text": "あんた、そんな技を隠し持ってたわけ！？\nもっと見せなさいよ！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_004_504_00620",
		"still_path_hash": "9072463264798612382",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 10,
		"localized_name": "イザナ",
		"romanized_name": "Izana",
		"model_path_hash": "3787596258689044991",
		"text": "あれー？　ヨハナ、さっきはマジックみたいな\nものだろう、って言ってたのに",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_048_504_00621",
		"still_path_hash": "4716347634718713212",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 11,
		"localized_name": "ヨハナ",
		"romanized_name": "Johanna",
		"model_path_hash": "5020305352148956270",
		"text": "はっ！？　う、うるさい！\n……期待以上だったから、少し興奮しただけ",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_004_504_00622",
		"still_path_hash": "9072463264798612382",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 12,
		"localized_name": "鬼門",
		"romanized_name": "Kimon",
		"model_path_hash": "4093314950907503731",
		"text": "ライブでボーっとしてたら、見失うかも？\nだから、よーく拙者を見てるでござるよ！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_181_504_00623",
		"still_path_hash": "6299303620813546084",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 13,
		"localized_name": "キューン",
		"romanized_name": "Quinn",
		"model_path_hash": "913274709521753211",
		"text": "……ふふっ",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_200_504_00624",
		"still_path_hash": "7374237645965483172",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 14,
		"localized_name": "ベップ",
		"romanized_name": "Bepp",
		"model_path_hash": "3101416597918110218",
		"text": "わ。急に笑って……何を見てるの？\nもしかして鏡かしら",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_151_504_00625",
		"still_path_hash": "5045460652135134961",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 15,
		"localized_name": "キューン",
		"romanized_name": "Quinn",
		"model_path_hash": "913274709521753211",
		"text": "そんな面白い顔してるかな！？",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_200_504_00626",
		"still_path_hash": "7374237645965483172",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 16,
		"localized_name": "ヤドヴィガ",
		"romanized_name": "Jadwiga",
		"model_path_hash": "2111970354351478659",
		"text": "本日アップされた、\n『Ｃｕｔｉｅ☆ＡｎｉｍａＬ』の動画と認識",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_199_504_00627",
		"still_path_hash": "6170794110252514656",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 17,
		"localized_name": "ベップ",
		"romanized_name": "Bepp",
		"model_path_hash": "3101416597918110218",
		"text": "『Ｃｕｔｉｅ☆ＡｎｉｍａＬ』？",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_151_504_00628",
		"still_path_hash": "5045460652135134961",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 18,
		"localized_name": "キューン",
		"romanized_name": "Quinn",
		"model_path_hash": "913274709521753211",
		"text": "うん。最近デビューしたアイドルユニットなんだって",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_200_504_00629",
		"still_path_hash": "7374237645965483172",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 19,
		"localized_name": "ヤドヴィガ",
		"romanized_name": "Jadwiga",
		"model_path_hash": "2111970354351478659",
		"text": "公式ＳＮＳの情報によれば、彼女たちも\nカウントダウンフェスの審査枠に応募した模様",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_199_504_00630",
		"still_path_hash": "6170794110252514656",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 20,
		"localized_name": "ベップ",
		"romanized_name": "Bepp",
		"model_path_hash": "3101416597918110218",
		"text": "なるほど。ライバルってことね。\n負けるわけにはいかないわ",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_151_504_00631",
		"still_path_hash": "5045460652135134961",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 21,
		"localized_name": "キューン",
		"romanized_name": "Quinn",
		"model_path_hash": "913274709521753211",
		"text": "でも、見て……これ",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_200_504_00632",
		"still_path_hash": "7374237645965483172",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 22,
		"localized_name": "キューン",
		"romanized_name": "Quinn",
		"model_path_hash": "913274709521753211",
		"text": "ふふ。なんだか、笑顔になれるね",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_200_504_00633",
		"still_path_hash": "7374237645965483172",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	}
]